Ben was blown away. "So the Charms just flew away! Like, they exist now??"\par
She nodded seriously, "Yep. Which means there's potential for more baddies like Hex to abuse them."\par
"At least no-one'll have all five, not for a while. So the chance of abuse is lessened." Max said.\par
"And the Keystone...flew at you?" Ben asked, looking his cousin carefully over.\par
"Yeah. I don't know where it went but that's when I passed out."\par
Ben excitedly yelled, "I still can't believe that you found some spell on the Internet and saved the day with it! That's not bad work for a hero!" \par
"Ex-hero. But thanks."\par
"Hey, you're still a hero - powers or no powers."\par
